      "name": "How long does it take to develop a website?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Website development typically takes 2-6 weeks depending on complexity. Simple business websites can be completed in 2-3 weeks, while complex e-commerce or custom web applications may take 4-6 weeks."
